name: Stash
description:
Sarah Gwan starter logos are the perfect kick-start for your new business!

HOW IT WORKS: 
after purchase, send us the name exactly as you’d like it to appear, along with any color changes. One color change and one name change are included, no font changes.

email: sarahgwan@gmail.com

We will customize the logo, and send a proof within 48 hours.

Once approved, you will receive the following files:

• JPG (hi-res) 
• PNG (transparent background) 
• EPS (vector) 
• Layered PSD (for future changes) 
• Font information (no fonts will be sent)

*The names and photos used with the logo are not included.

All logo designs are Copyright © sarahgwan.com 
They are not for resale or to be incorporated into designs for resale.
